Mm-hmm.

38:14.346 --> 38:16.711
Amen!

38:18.857 --> 38:20.519
Amen!

38:22.761 --> 38:25.383
Is there anything

38:25.417 --> 38:27.495
that God can't do?

38:29.857 --> 38:31.647
There is nothing

38:31.681 --> 38:33.855
our God can't do!

38:35.136 --> 38:37.407
Hallelujah!

38:38.127 --> 38:40.012
Hallelujah!

38:42.295 --> 38:44.820
<i>There is nothing</i>

38:44.854 --> 38:47.828
<i>that our God can't do!</i>

38:52.656 --> 38:55.181
Must be nice going straight
from the papers to the pulpit

38:55.215 --> 38:57.165
without skipping a beat.

38:57.199 --> 38:59.117
Shameless.

38:59.151 --> 39:02.476
Pastor Skanks, shouldn't you be
downtown tending your flock?

39:02.511 --> 39:05.933
