of mutual edification.

39:17.527 --> 39:19.445
That would be biblical.

39:19.480 --> 39:21.046
Not really your style.

39:21.080 --> 39:23.541
So you want to talk about the Bible?

39:23.575 --> 39:25.638
Let's talk about commandments.

39:25.698 --> 39:27.200
What's your message, boy?

39:27.234 --> 39:28.671
You're going down.

39:30.618 --> 39:31.896
I'm gonna pull you like a weed

39:31.929 --> 39:34.807
and throw you onto God's fire
where you belong.

39:37.893 --> 39:39.620
What do you have against me?

39:42.873 --> 39:44.919
You don't know?

39:45.792 --> 39:47.199
You killed my daddy.

39:51.069 --> 39:52.987
You're Daryl James' boy?

39:53.021 --> 39:54.426
I am.

40:01.724 --> 40:04.955
And by the time I'm done
with you, Bishop,

40:04.988 --> 40:08.314
the only thing that's gonna
rise to heaven from this church

40:09.060 --> 40:10.499
